{"type": "article", "id": 50610, "title": "复星竞购La Perla失败，以及，Jo Malone 的春季新款很美 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2018-02-27T03:37:38Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 37799, "name": "祖马龙"}, {"id": 48044, "name": "CONVERSE"}, {"id": 2969, "name": "Vivienne Westwood"}, {"id": 23124, "name": "SMEG"}, {"id": 3110, "name": "D&G"}, {"id": 2855, "name": "Tommy Hilfiger"}, {"id": 5170, "name": "Moncler"}, {"id": 346, "name": "La Perla"}, {"id": 24250, "name": "Jacquemus"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 31, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180227112607uiKy2DqcOArtpjWs.jpg", "contents": "<h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/sapinda-buys-la-perla-from-pacific-global-1202595695/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>荷兰私募基金收购高端内衣品牌 La Perla</strong></a> | 日前，荷兰私募基金 Sapinda Holding 从意大利企业家 Silvio Sacaglia 手上 100% 收购了 La Perla。有意收购 La Perla 的另一潜在买家复星集团竞购失败，有<a href=\"https://www.businessoffashion.com/articles/news-analysis/sapinda-buys-la-perla\" rel=\"nofollow\">消息</a>称双方就是否将生产线移出欧洲出现分歧。这笔交易并未透露具体金额。</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/moncler-sales-near-1-2-billion-euros-1202596298/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Moncler 去年收入大涨至 11.9 亿欧元</strong></a> | 截止至 12 月 31 日的十二个月内，Moncler 的收入大涨 15%，至 11.9 亿欧元。受所有市场和渠道的强劲表现推动，全年净利润增长了 27%，至 2.497 亿欧元。</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/fashion-scoops/simon-porte-jacquemus-launches-mens-collection-1202596108/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>法国设计师品牌 Jacquemus 将推出男装线</strong></a> | 周一，设计师 Simon Porte Jacquemus 在他的女装发布会上宣布，将推出一个男装线，新的男装产品计划在六月的巴黎时装周推出。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180227111729MLBj72hYsmeuDpbk.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.648438\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>美国设计师品牌 <a href=\"http://uk.fashionnetwork.com/news/Rebecca-Minkoff-launches-swim-line,952024.html#.WpTG2JP1UzU\" rel=\"nofollow\">Rebecca Minkoff </a>推出首个泳装线。设计师 Minkoff 解释称，花了两年时间打造这个系列，以吸引城市和沿海地带的时髦女孩。 </p><p>该系列将于 3 月 1 日正式推出，价格从 70 至 145 美元不等。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802271120136kDWV3L18fjprN4X.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.648438\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180227112014Ls7u38vepkHElVjc.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>米兰时装周上，为庆祝与梅赛德斯 AMG 车队正式达成合作关系，<a href=\"https://www.businessoffashion.com/articles/fashion-show-review/tommy-hilfiger-hits-the-track\" rel=\"nofollow\">Tommy Hilfiger</a> 不光在 2018 春夏系列新品中加入了很多的赛车元素，还把秀场打造成了跑道。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180227112032LqIsUTDNnP8cWd0Y.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802271120460qt6PEwfIo1KlzpJ.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180227112032rfNRhjFoCWxAeOaw.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180227112033KmiaS18pZl4DVQCP.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180227112033GAf8pHhkDNr130P5.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802271120334dHqkECXFRKJGP7t.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802271120339mqsVMBlG8duXnSY.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180227112033xuqHnLrwNAsVvptf.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180227112033zS32fIU4ME5KJX91.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180227112045vyph5LA19biYlJcr.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180227112045ryvtNwaKLiOHD6Xl.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180227112045TkjLqpIXVH8EdrYC.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180227112046SoJalpvNGMzDuyX8.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180227112046anE4t7YVmlX1KJcb.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180227112046PvF7Rkc2gwm1oLVt.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180227112046ln05UD718QjNFgOo.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180227112046TgWh5DU2VSqOxmrX.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180227112046YKl4qUAEDwOu8tI1.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180227112046WsSrGCNludiqe2zk.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802271120464SmOqdEsJ7UygucW.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180227112046tuVYKL2SMlD6wRPr.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180227112046OuqpG01geNToQFcA.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802271120465jf4kRMSYKe9vFrh.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://www.highsnobiety.com/p/jw-anderson-converse-sneaker-collab/#slide-5\" rel=\"nofollow\">J.W Anderson 和 Converse 联名系列</a>新款将于 3 月 2 日正式推出。这一波新品以 Converse’s Chuck 70 和 Thunderbolt silhouettes 为原型打造，鞋身以麂皮制作。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180227112120FxaJOWbDh8dKgYEP.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180227112111657r1ljMvSsJ2eKN.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180227112111uBgbCjFURrQWcKEy.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180227112113nUu6RsqATkPZCyVv.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180227112127TKPkmXxJoLHNUnSa.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180227112127xtYVPEiqCSnOmabh.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180227112128WPVYcaHwp0Ax6vTQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180227112132zcLPwWUpah81kHfs.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://www.highsnobiety.com/2018/02/25/dolce-and-gabbana-kitchen-appliances/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dolce&amp;Gabbana 与 smeg 合作</a>的厨房用具系列正式发售。该系列包括烤面包机、咖啡机、水壶、搅拌机等，以意大利南部风格的印花图案装饰，风格浮夸华丽。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180227112144jbqrPlJWi1a9Adys.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802271121446M7gSaC3xH2N9ovY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180227112149WZ9VoJYF6mTfirHb.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180227112149zOyo1NDILaEkStqX.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>西太后<a href=\"https://www.fashionsnap.com/article/2018-02-26/sk8-hi2vivienne-westwood-anglomania/\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Vivienne Westwood 和 VANS 合作，</a>以 sk8-Hi 为原型，打造了风格不同的鞋款。 </p><p>这个系列将于 3 月 23 日登陆日本市场，售价 1 万 9000 日元。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180227112206jak7t56bEdpFBJXU.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.989394\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180227112205AtgySr1U3cQPbFBM.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180227112205HShyVnImDQNYktBw.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180227112213V1NZFrXoldbGtkCU.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180227112205EX3KYOki2DuBFe6t.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180227112213geOBjhNVJnKxDwHM.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>2 月 28 日即将上架的 <a href=\"https://www.mobile01.com/newsdetail/24334/jomalonelondon-jml-englishfields\" rel=\"nofollow\">Jo Malone London</a> 春季限量款看起来很美。 </p><p>这个系列首次以谷物为主要元素，并推出了特别的陶瓷拼色瓶身，一共五款香调，分别是燕麦与矢车菊、樱草花与黑麦、青麦与绣线菊、罂粟花与大麦、蜂蜜与藏红花，充满了英国田园的调调。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180227112236RGtxpLV6oXQMq5YZ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180227112230zMh315C6FTgVWY7A.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.881944\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180227112232WRLPChksIBxmbztg.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802271122266pyfVmcK0SWihNO9.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.760833\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><br></p><p>题图来自：Jo Malone</p>"}